---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'January 10, 2026';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="GasTag privacy policy - we respect your privacy and collect no personal data.">
  <Navigation />

  <main class="pt-16">
    <section class="py-16">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-500 mb-12">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

        <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Overview</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            GasTag is designed with your privacy in mind. We do not collect, store, or transmit any personal data or usage analytics. Your gas readings and labels stay on your device.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Data Collection</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            <strong>We collect no data.</strong> The GasTag app does not:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Collect personal information</li>
            <li>Track your location</li>
            <li>Use analytics or tracking services</li>
            <li>Require account creation</li>
            <li>Send data to any servers</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Bluetooth Usage</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            GasTag uses Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE) to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Connect to the GasTag Bridge hardware to receive gas readings</li>
            <li>Connect to your Brother label printer to print tank labels</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Bluetooth connections are made only with devices you explicitly choose to pair with. No data is transmitted over the internet.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Local Storage</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Gas readings and analysis history are stored locally on your iPhone. This data is not backed up to iCloud and is deleted when you uninstall the app.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            The GasTag app does not integrate with any third-party services, analytics platforms, or advertising networks.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            GasTag does not collect any information from anyone, including children under 13.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            If we make changes to this privacy policy, we will update the "Last updated" date at the top of this page.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at chad@2kgt.com.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
